  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 2160 mg
time required: 30 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/szechuan-pork-noodle-stir-fry-64a4f7393223226bfd2b8af3
cuisine: Asian
